Why is the <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">hundred</ENAMEX> - pacer seen as the quintessential <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Taiwanese</ENAMEX> snake ?
And how much do we know about this endangered species which has been designated a " rare cultural resource " ?
