Traditional <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Paiwan</ENAMEX> beliefs include many spirits .
The <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">hundred</ENAMEX> - pace viper represents a guardian spirit who protects the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Paiwan</ENAMEX> in their homeland around <ENAMEX TYPE="LOC">Mt. Tawu</ENAMEX> .
