In the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Paiwan</ENAMEX> village of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Pingho</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</ENAMEX> most important festivals was <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">the Hundred - Pacer Festival</ENAMEX> , which used to be held once every ten years .
