Other <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Taiwanese</ENAMEX> aboriginal peoples with a close relationship to the <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">hundred</ENAMEX> - pacer are the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Bunun</ENAMEX> and the <ENAMEX TYPE="NORP">Rukai</ENAMEX> .
